        <body>
            <div type="question">
                <p>Imagine your life in 10 years time. What will it look like?</p>
                <note type="word-limit">(at least 60 words)</note>
                <label type="level">
                    <span>A2</span>
                </label>
            </div>
            <div type="answer">
                <p>In 10 years time, I would like to be a famous journalist and travel around the world. I really enjoy travelling because I love moving and discover new things. But I also like to be informed and know what is happening in the world. In fact, I think that it is important to know the issues of our world and to try to find solutions about it.</p>
            </div>
            <div type="grading">
                <label corresp="#examiner.1" subtype="writing" type="level">
                    <span>B1</span>
                    <note type="comment"/>
                </label>
                <label corresp="#examiner.2" subtype="writing" type="level">
                    <span>B1</span>
                    <note type="comment">Not enough text to judge whether B2 or  B1. B2 vocab and structures.</note>
                </label>
                <label corresp="#examiner.3" subtype="writing" type="level">
                    <span>B1</span>
                    <note type="comment"/>
                </label>
                <label subtype="majority-vote" type="level">
                    <span>B1</span>
                </label>
            </div>
